reviews.review_text: Listen to the false start Brokedown Palace Jerry starts singing the wrong line, then apologizes to the crowd, it's very funny.  Overall a great show, they always pulled it off in Europe.
Nice This is a really good show, the first set is sweet! Look at that song list, for chrissakes. Worth a DL, IMHO.
